{"type": "article", "id": 53977, "title": "有个啥都能做的智能衣架，长的样子倒是蛮可爱的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-06-05T23:11:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 50884, "name": "Aronson’s Floor Covering"}, {"id": 33630, "name": "Vibia"}, {"id": 16699, "name": "RIMOWA"}, {"id": 50885, "name": "Off-White™"}, {"id": 50559, "name": "Pasquè Dudley Mawalla"}, {"id": 50886, "name": "Kenton Lee"}, {"id": 50887, "name": "Ghislaine Viñas"}, {"id": 33631, "name": "Arik Levy"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 135, "image": "img/article/article_show/201806060711093J7ciVqE8F52pz4U.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>RIMOWA x Off-White™ </h3><p>为庆祝品牌成立 120 周年，德国顶级箱包品牌 RIMOWA 推出与潮牌 Off-White™ 的合作系列，即三款主打产品 Original，Essential 以及 Essential LITE 的升级更新版本，这也是品牌迄今重量最轻的行李箱。</p><p>联名款采用全透明聚碳酸酯制作的 Essential 行李箱，两个尺寸更分别以 “PERSONAL” 和 “BELONGINGS” 字样凸显 Off-White™ 品牌特色，配以 “MISCELLANEOUS” 隔层，同时还有一个便携洗漱包推出。全透明的设计风格，也是为了让消费者参与到设计过程。据官网介绍，这次的联名系列将于 6 月 25 日开始在 RIMOWA 与 Off-White™ 全球指定门店、RIMOWA 欧洲官方网站以及微信线上快闪店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193625G0DTkCIJfvi4cXpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193625hdfH8mOeaR0QGMxP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665557\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806051936258qit1QjGpUOsRL4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666297\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193626cOaswLzWfI7joShD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018060519362658INodQOfUVmznrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666297\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2018/6/off-white-rimowa-rethought-product-line-launch\" rel=\"nofollow\">HYPEBEAST</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Take-Off</h3><p>最近，众筹网站 Kickstarter 上线了一款名为 Take-Off 的智能衣架，其采用木质机身，通过 5 个可自动翻牌卡片做为“屏幕”来显示时间、温度和穿衣信息。</p><p>当用户把衣物挂在 Take Off 顶端，Take Off 就会自动开启对应相关衣物的清洁模式，包括清洁时间、温度等，然后喷出蒸汽清洁衣服，同时也会释放出负离子，清除衣服上的臭味和细菌。此外，Take-Off 还可以自动获取天气数据，如果是阴雨天或是雨雪天，它会提醒你多加衣服。当然，它还会告诉你室外温度，让你提前做好准备。</p><p>此外，Take-Off 还配有一个手持式吸尘器和四种不同质料的刷头，可清洁衣服上的灰尘。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g06783zdf2o&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193820Pyf58aeQvF6LlEDk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562724\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193705CNGhulw2J1eRKjDX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193705wg8X2hed4Ki9Gbj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193705hbGq86IgMetHpZUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193705rgsKYXADElxa06pC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.769524\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/06/04/a-smart-hanger-that-recommends-clothes-based-on-the-weather-forecast/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Rhythm Chandelier By Arik Levy for Vibia</h3><p>巴塞罗那照明品牌 Vibia 推出了一系列名为 Rhythm 的枝形吊灯，操刀设计的是以色列裔法国设计师 Arik Levy，灵感来自禅宗和极简主义。</p><p>它的结构方式很灵活，每个灯杆都可以通过其轴心旋转，锁定到任意位置。光线投射的角度和吊灯的形状，具体取决于灯杆的尺寸，这也意味着 Rhythm 吊灯能够适用于很多场合，既可以提供常规的周边照明和向下聚光照明功能，也可以提供间接照明功能。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193907sfm4ztvYbji3Q05r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193907vwWmYL5iaBhJQAGS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.993976\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193908uexMsmcaptI7wQgF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.002012\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193908kQbh6f3wu5F0JIcR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.002008\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Empire Collection by Ghislaine Viñas for Aronson’s Floor Covering</h3><p>美国地毯与地板制造商 Aronson’s Floor Covering 推出 Empire 系列地毯，其设计师是在室内设计界颇有声誉的家装设计师 Ghislaine Viñas。</p><p>Ghislaine Viñas 一直相信色彩的能量，在这个手工精品地毯系列中，还是延续了她的标志性风格，融合了大胆的色彩和极具表现力的图案，灵感均是源自设计师在纽约生活 28 年的点滴回忆，包括邻里街巷的元素，自己住的阁楼，交通繁忙的高速公路以及闲缓散步的哈德逊河步道等等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193933GHT7tNQ9g2EydfIS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193934bS0Yw92L15X6ZgeN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193933YDTQFL9ao0U2HEXc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.778333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806051939340OBdDwJjGKxsL26y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193935vGhWCDx59toQTNMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605193935qfn2pjZ5GDHJYu1r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.762000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018060519393676fivDe4UELzKOQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://aronsonsfloors.com/products/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aronson’s Floor Covering</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Shoe That Grows by Kenton Lee</h3><p>对于很多低收入家庭来说，孩子成长期所需的服饰鞋履都是一笔不小的开销。肯尼亚设计师 Kenton Lee 创立了一个名为“会长大的鞋”（The Shoe That Grows）的公益项目，其中的核心产品，就是一双可以改变尺寸的鞋。</p><p>它利用柔软的橡胶材质和可调节的纽扣设计，让鞋子的大小可以随穿着者的脚码而改变，一双鞋子可以调整为五个尺码，伴随孩子成长几年。每双鞋 10 美元，便宜的价格让很多人都有能力购买，设计师也鼓励更多人购买该鞋捐赠给贫困地区的孩子们。<a href=\"https://theshoethatgrows.org/distribute-shoes-survey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=f0678itte1g&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194019oFKaOPeJsxqcbhzC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194019celRFtMVvZyikjGu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806051940205rpMHgPkmR8Q7VFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201806051940208A157SyWFLYawkjB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194020zkyJA0rYOIdwqlj2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194020IfKNye4v0Ah5SW9U.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Seron Side Table by Pasquè Dudley Mawalla</h3><p>坦桑尼亚设计师 Pasquè Dudley Mawalla 推出了一款名为 Seron 的边桌，它的特别之处在于支撑桌面的结构，除了一条曲折结构的桌腿，还有一个底面，灵感来自于街头艺人的表演。</p><p>这种独特的平衡设计，鼓励用户思考其保持直立背后的设计巧思。此外，边桌的底面也成为了放置、收纳书籍杂志的好去处。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194046PSYgwbh8cMLo6DJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194046BreyMK3zATSZ7Wil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194046jq3uHmPec6n2wf0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180605194046KXBD6UHyfLh28xpO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664762\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/06/05/this-side-table-is-a-sideshow-of-its-own/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}